 the standard rule, as long as they have a reasonable Primary Rule justification
, such as using flight to swoop down a enemy while swinging an Electric
 Mace to add the speed of the dive to the impact of the mace.
 Each Ability contributing takes one Action.
 You can't combine more than 
\series bold
two
\series default
