\begin_layout Standard
Besides attacking to Out, you can attack to Disable one of the opponent's
 Abilities.
 The attacker rolls normally, following the Primary Rule, and the defender
 rolls the Ability instead of whatever defense would normally be applicable
 (so it's easier to Disable weaker Abilities).
 A Hinder
