At Combat Range all Abilities work normally; at Pursuit Range, the you can
 only roll a Contest of either movement vs.
 movement or sensory Abilities versus hiding or evasion; if you've Lost
 Contact, you can't even try to locate the target any more—you have no idea
 which direction they've gone or how far.
 What constitutes Combat Range does 
\emph on
