\begin_layout Standard
Negotiations are a catch-all for all inter-personal interaction that is
 not overtly hostile.
 Usually, you want something from someone else, and are trying to convince
 them to give it to you, whether you want a possession, information, or
 simply for them not to help your enemies.
\end_layout

